    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been absolutely pampered, looks flawless inside and out, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019ve been searching for a ride that\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom condition, this is definitely the one. I've taken such good care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
