    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to exacting standards. The 3.2L inline-six exhibits factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the critical rod bearing and double-VANOS services already documented. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is free of subframe fatigue, featuring reinforced mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry with Bilstein B16 dampers. Every bushing remains pliable, and the throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is instantaneous. Finished in immaculate Titanium Silver over Nappa leather, this is a turnkey, investment-grade machine for the discerning driver who values mechanical integrity and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
