    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage since the day it left the dealership. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized service centers. It has never seen inclement weather and has been hand-washed only using the two-bucket method. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a like-new example of this model.",
